Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是拍不到哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的战斗都有直播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为以桐人的性格 最初开始就会冲出来打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不… 别看那家伙那样 他其实挺会算计的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许在等参加人数减少 哪里躲着呢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是桐人也不会那么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 爸爸的话 一定以摄像机都拍不到的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间从敌人的背后偷袭 打倒敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真说不定呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且明明是枪的游戏 却不用抢 非用剑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像哥哥的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝衣服的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是这次的优胜候补之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这不是不成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没被打倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是让对方一定时间内麻痹的攻击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像风魔法的「封雷网」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:55.02,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(640,543)}「死枪」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:55.02,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,489)\blur2\fs35}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音 开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？打哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打那个破披风的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了！狙了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他开枪之前！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发觉到我的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里看到过我 被系统判定为可识别了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:34.59,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\p1\an5\fscx827\fscy375\pos(723,51)}m 0 0 l -10 -6 l -10 -6 l 10 -6 l 10 6 l -10 6 l -10 -6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:34.59,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8\c&H000000&}失去连接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和这把枪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正名字是死枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(743,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…早晚…也会出现在你们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…用这把枪…给你们带去真正的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拥有…这个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还…没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…还都…没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's show time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在哪里见过那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到底是在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 只可能是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾恩葛朗特里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗…骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那家伙是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不…之前的名字我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是 「微笑棺木」的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(666,670)}Laughing Coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑棺木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(640,670)}Laughing Coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说那家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用菜刀的那个队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不…不是PoH
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和PoH的说话方式和态度都完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是刚才的 It's show time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是PoH最喜欢的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是PoH身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领导层的干部玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没错 那家伙就是死枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(832,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死枪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(632,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是传闻中 被他射过的玩家再也没有上线过的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 他用某种方法将玩家真的杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实世界中已经有2个人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没现身…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…你继续监视桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就确认那家伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么短的时间就移动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个破斗篷没有显示在终端上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一样潜到到河里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话 他现在的武器应该全部解除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着一把手枪的话应该也能在水里移动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是那样 只有一把手枪的话我们可以轻松的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也看到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用那把黑手枪将Pale Rider杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被打中 说不定就真的死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有玩家不是单纯的PK而是真的将人杀死这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个破斗篷死枪他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(723,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我以前经历的VRMMO中杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我以前经历的VRMMO中杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道对方会死 还是挥动着手中的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙…真的在…GGO…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事 只是有点被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 你所说的我没办法马上相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不认为你说的都是胡编乱造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 如果我们不马上离开这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为我们正在交战的其他玩家会凑过来坐收渔翁之利的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们在此分别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么打算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去追死枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(701,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音 你尽量不要去靠近他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会遵守约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见到你时我会全力与你一战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你没有攻击我听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死枪那家伙很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(515,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果输给他还怎么和我战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也不愿意 我们还是暂时一起行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把他踢出决赛才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那家伙真的很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都不知道死枪在哪里 在不在一起还不是一样危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(448,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来要先解决这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来进攻 掩护就交给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在 诗音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死枪应该会沿河北上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(495,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在出现下一个牺牲者之前我想阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音 有没有什么好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他有什么神奇的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从根本上来说是狙击手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很不擅长掩护较少的开阔地带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉他应该是要去那座城市的废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们也朝着城市前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在SAO 大家都坚守着无论什么情况也不能让HP全损
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 HP归零时人就会真的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 微笑棺木的人却杀了数十
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…是数百人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我们攻略组采取行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组成讨伐队想要将他们抓获…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该也在前线战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很惨烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他从昨晚开始就有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许…他是为了解决以前的宿怨才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不是说打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要先下线了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先联系一下桐人的委托人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委托人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是让桐人进入GGO的那个人 肯定会知道些什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我不在的这段时间能不能找一下和GGO有关的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么各位 请稍等我一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没追上死枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(701,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是我们追过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是边跑边注意水里的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那么他现在应该藏在城市的某处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河在这里就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 那就在下次的扫描中确定死枪的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(842,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他攻击其他人之前进行强攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样虽然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不要忘了死枪并不是他真正的用户名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(536,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得第一次上场的诗音你不了解的有3人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这中间Pale Rider并不是死枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(852,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是还剩下2人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪士X或是Sterben的其中一人就是他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们两个都在这里 我们可没时间去考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 刚才我突然想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把“枪士”反过来读就是“死枪” 死枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(408,670)}jyuushi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(819,670)}shijyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(957,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X是十字架画十字的手势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(553,670)}Cross
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…这么想是不是太白痴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过角色名之类的大家不都那感觉的么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从本名上拽字编的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 两个人都在的话就去枪士X那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我和PealRider一样被麻痹了 你也别慌张进入狙击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死枪一定会出来 用那把黑色手枪了结我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(282,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓那个时机狙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打的可能是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会那么狙我这事 我早就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧吧 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了哦…伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你协力可只有这会哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人 你从北边开始找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在这个城市里的只有枪士X
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Sterben不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 枪士X就是死枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(828,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他盯着的大概是这人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得在莉心进入死枪的射程之前阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(598,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 掩护交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子还在等莉心出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 现在开始从他背后突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音在运动场前面的大楼里进入狙击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有你的掩护我才能无所畏惧地冲锋陷阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组合不就是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在与你分头30s后开始战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点时间够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 足够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒了死枪 那家伙就会变回敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(551,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狙了他 打倒他 然后 忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那家伙 一定不会再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死枪应该在运动场内才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(455,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人 你是真的 还是冒牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子就能真相大白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 疯狂厮杀的你的样子我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个女人 你的同伴杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你和那时候一样发疯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人 来吧 让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愤怒…杀意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂气的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.30,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(450,450)}黑星54式：「54式黑星」仿制苏联TT生产的国产枪  因为便宜深受国外痞子喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑星…54式…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把枪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…在这里…出现那把枪…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 死亡追击者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
